description:
This is a 27 minute workout called '25 MIN EXPRESS PILATES WORKOUT || Moderate to Intermediate Pilates (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
